                  </hi>.—He <hi rend="italic">was further charged with having been before convicted in April, 1861, in the name of <persName id="t18650130-name-251">
                        <interp inst="t18650130-name-251" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18650130-name-251" type="surname" value="SMITH"></interp>
